Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.70,0:00:21.66,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:17705,21668}Whenever my feelings were hurt,\NI couldn't see anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:25.58,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:21668,25588}because I held a lie in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:29.55,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:25588,29551}Time moved faster than I could react,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:34.59,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:29551,34597}so I pulled myself away\Nfrom everything, but now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:40.64,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:34597,40645}I can't stop anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:47.61,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:41062,47610}Accepting everything, I rise up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:53.49,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:49571,53491}I'll fly over all of time\Nwhile holding onto your presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:56.99,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:53491,56995}following the trace of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:01:03.00,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:56995,63001}My world becomes engulfed with light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:09.25,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:65461,69257}A never ending sky,\Nyour never changing eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:12.96,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:69257,72969}I want to love these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:19.35,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:72969,79350}No matter the distance,\Nor if we are separated
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.35,0:01:22.77,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:79350,82770}we are always connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:29.44,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:87066,89444}Want you here tonight!
Comment: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:31.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:91112,91112}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:15.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:129942,135156}UNFORGIVABLE!\NTHE BAD GUYS DESTROY A HOUSE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.03,0:02:24.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:141037,144082}– Good morning!\N– Good morning, Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,0:02:27.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:144332,147293}Hey, Meimi, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:29.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:147502,149420}This brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:32.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:149671,152799}Isn't this a Miho-chan doll?\NI had one like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:38.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153549,158805}I found it cleaning my room. It brought\Nback memories so I brought it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:42.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159055,162892}I wonder if I still have mine.\NI'll try looking for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:48.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:163142,168773}We girls have a lot of memories\Nin these dolls, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:52.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:169440,172819}You girls are lucky to have\Nthat much time on your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:55.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173027,175488}I don't even have time\Nto make memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.69,0:03:00.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175697,180284}I'm so busy trying\Nto catch St. Tail that…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:06.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:181494,186124}Right. With all those memories of\NSt. Tail escaping, you're frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:08.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:186708,188209}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:11.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188459,191879}If you don't like it,\Ntry catching her quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.13,0:03:16.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192130,196843}It'll be your most precious memory.\NThough it's probably impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:22.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:197427,202140}Now you've said it! I'm not after\NSt. Tail for a reason like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:25.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202348,205476}Precious memories, what nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:30.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:205727,210773}Is that so? Are you saying there are\Nno memories between you and St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:34.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:212233,214235}Why are you so upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:37.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214485,217822}– How should I know?\N– My doll…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:43.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220616,223786}It disgusts me to know\Nwhat a dingbat that guy is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:48.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:224537,228750}Oh, my. We should be\Nthe ones appreciating him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:54.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:229542,234005}Why is that?\NHe's never done anything to save—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:57.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:235214,237842}That's not true, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:04:01.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238092,241971}When you're angry, Meimi,\Nit's usually about Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:04.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:242221,244140}Seira, you're mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:09.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244390,249020}Anyway, today there was another\Nlost sheep that wandered by here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:12.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:249854,252982}A while ago, Michiru came by\Nto ask for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:17.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:253232,257445}She used to live happily\Nin a mansion with her parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:23.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258029,263201}But one year ago, Michiru's father\Nco-signed a loan for a friend…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:27.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263451,267371}…and because of that,\Nthey lost their mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:31.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:268247,271709}That friend he co-signed for…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:35.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271918,275338}…took the loan money\Nand disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:40.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:276130,280468}Not only did the loan company\Ntake control of the mansion…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:43.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:280718,283304}…but everything inside\Nof it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:47.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284388,287433}Michiru's jewelry box\Nwas a precious thing…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:50.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287683,290269}…filled with all kinds of memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:54.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:290978,294315}Michiru hid the box in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:59.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294565,299654}Right after that, they were forced\Nto vacate the property.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:04.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:300404,304367}Then that jewelry box is\Nstill hidden in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:08.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:305952,308579}She was planning to get it back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.83,0:05:11.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:308830,311833}But Negoro, who owns\Nthe loan company…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:21.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:315920,321300}It's you again. You'll get nowhere,\Nno matter how many times you come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:23.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:321509,323678}Just for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:27.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:323928,327431}I want to see the inside\Nof the house one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:32.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:327682,332687}This house doesn't belong to you\Nanymore, young lady. It's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:36.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:333771,336983}Also, this land is being sold…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:41.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337233,341362}…so we're gonna have\Nto tear down the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:47.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:341904,347076}What will happen to her memories?\NThe jewelry box of memories?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:53.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:347910,353040}There's nothing that can be done\Nabout Michiru's house being torn down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:58.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:353624,358004}Then at least the jewelry box\Nshould be returned to Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:06:00.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:358838,360923}If it isn't, it'll be too sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:05.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:361173,365469}Ever since the house was taken,\NMichiru's mother has become ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:09.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:366804,369515}They're breaking down\Nthe house tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:11.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:369765,371934}We only have tonight\Nto carry this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:14.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:372310,374770}Let's get those memories back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:23.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:382403,383613}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:32.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391037,392872}Is this a…?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:36.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393289,396250}"Tonight, I'll be entering\Nthe Misaki mansion…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:38.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:396500,398961}…to pick up a jewelry box.\N– St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:41.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:399170,401505}It's a notice from St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:44.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401714,404675}– A notice from St. Tail?\N– Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:48.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:404926,408638}Don't push. I can't see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:06:59.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:416771,419398}So that's the Misaki mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:04.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422276,424111}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:10.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426739,430785}– I'll leave tomorrow up to you.\N– I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:22.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:436248,442296}This is really troublesome, isn't it?\NTearing down a mansion like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:27.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442546,447343}Making this an open lot is the terms\Nthe buyer made. What can I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:29.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:447593,449553}It'll all be done by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:32.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:449804,452473}We're finally getting to the cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:38.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452723,458312}Didn't think that it'd go this smooth.\NLike a bubble on a wet hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:42.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458562,462775}Nobody would suspect that\Nyou borrowed the money and I lent it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:45.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463567,465861}Not realizing a thing…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:50.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:466070,470658}…your co-signer Misaki is\Neither a real nice guy or an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:56.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:470908,476622}– Oh, how my heart aches.\N– That guy picked a bad friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:59.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:476872,479917}– Speak for yourself.\N– Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:01.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480167,481836}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:07.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:482086,487508}Mr. Negoro? I'm Asuka Jr. I'm assisting\Nin the St. Tail investigations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:09.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:488009,489635}St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:13.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:489885,493764}Actually, we just received\Na notice from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:18.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:494015,498227}She's going to appear here tonight\Nto steal a jewelry box.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:21.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498811,501480}A jewelry box? Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:25.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501731,505526}How could there be such a thing\Nin this unoccupied mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:27.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:505776,507945}By the way, what's that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:30.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508195,510614}Tomorrow we're clearing this lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:33.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510823,513367}You're going to tear it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:40.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516203,520374}If St. Tail is coming, there will\Nbe a horde of cops here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:43.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:520624,523878}I know.\NAnyway, you'd better disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:47.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524086,527339}But is there really\Na jewelry box in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.09,0:08:52.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:528090,532595}I got everything in there out.\NThere shouldn't be anything left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:55.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:532845,535473}Something's fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:59.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535723,539310}St. Tail wouldn't come to steal\Nsomething that's not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:02.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540144,542271}Could she have uncovered our scheme?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:07.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:542521,547276}And the proof is hidden in this\Nmansion? And she's coming to steal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.07,0:09:14.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:549070,554658}St. Tail has caused many criminals\Nto be arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:19.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:555409,559080}Maybe we should clear\Nthe lot off tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:22.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:559288,562833}Whatever St. Tail is up to,\Nif there's no place here…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:25.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563084,565419}…there's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:29.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565878,569715}If the mansion isn't here,\Nthere's nothing that can be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:33.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:569965,573969}Since it's been decided,\Nlet's tear it down right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:36.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:574720,576013}Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:38.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:576263,578724}It's a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:41.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:578974,581685}Hey, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:44.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:581936,584855}What's all the panic about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:47.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585106,587733}Look! Doesn't this\Nbring back memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:51.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:587983,591237}It's the Miho-chan doll\Nthat you bought for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:52.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591487,592988}I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.23,0:09:58.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:593239,598119}I bought it for your fifth birthday.\NYou've had it all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:10:01.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:598369,601705}This doll was so very precious\Nto you, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:06.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:601956,606293}You didn't want any doll\Nother than this Miho-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:10.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:606544,610840}Papa, can you make this doll\Nnew again with your magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:16.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:611632,616095}Well, let's see. I wonder if I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:22.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618013,622059}But your precious memories\Nmay disappear too, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:26.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:624061,626897}Well, I'll keep it the way it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:28.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627314,628607}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:40.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:636448,640035}I'm sorry, I've got to go to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:44.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:640244,644540}So please entertain our guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:58.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:655384,658512}You're joking!\NI can't let you do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:03.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:659013,663517}Why? We've got to complete\Nthe clearing of the lot by tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:05.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:663767,665603}Get out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:08.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:665853,668731}You said it'd be done tomorrow,\Ndidn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.93,0:11:10.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:668939,670733}The plans have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:14.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670941,674612}St. Tail's coming!\NThere's no time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.11,0:11:18.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:675112,678240}She can take anything she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:21.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:678490,681535}What could be\Nin an empty house anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:25.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:681785,685039}A jewelry box. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:30.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685289,690544}Then please let us check if there\Nis really a jewelry box in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:33.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:691587,693130}There isn't one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:36.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693380,696800}Well, if it's not there,\NI'm clearing the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:41.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:697259,701013}But should we find one,\Nyou'll have to leave things to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:43.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:701263,703807}If stolen things are in there…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:48.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:704058,708103}…we have an obligation\Nto protect them from St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:51.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:708604,711190}You won't find one.
Comment: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:51.77,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:711774,711774}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:11:56.77,0:11:56.77,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:716779,716779}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:04.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:720783,724328}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.33,0:12:11.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:729333,731085}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.67,0:12:14.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:732670,734338}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:18.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736006,738676}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:34.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:752481,754775}St. Tail, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:40.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755025,760030}I don't know why, but they're\Nplanning to clear the lot tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:42.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:760281,762658}You're kidding! But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.86,0:12:47.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:762866,767204}I've checked up a bit\Non that loan company…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:49.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:767454,769873}…and it seems to be a little shady.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:53.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:770582,773085}Meimi, be very careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:58.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:773502,778299}Don't worry. I'll be back\Nwith Michiru's box of memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:04.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:780801,784305}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:08.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785806,788559}Please let me get there in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:16.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:793689,796150}Well? There's nothing here, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:33.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:808787,813625}Now, are you satisfied?\NSt. Tail has probably made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:37.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:813876,817963}I'll be keeping you to your promise\Nand start clearing the lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:40.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:818630,820674}I haven't said it's not here yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:45.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821300,825095}A promise is a promise.\NI won't stand for this any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:47.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:825346,827890}The work is going to be started.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:50.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:829058,830392}Even if I stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:53.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830642,833103}You should be careful\Nof the chandelier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:56.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:833354,836607}It'll probably come falling\Nwith the tremor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:04.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:842488,844281}What a stubborn idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:12.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849953,852956}Stop it! Stop it right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:14.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:853207,854666}What a pesky brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:19.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:856377,859338}What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:21.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:859588,861840}It's St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:29.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:867054,869556}Everyone! Get to your positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.14,0:14:41.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:879149,881276}That's St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:45.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:881527,885197}Knock her down with the bulldozer!\NNever mind! I'll do it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:50.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:887658,890452}How terrible can he get?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.91,0:14:56.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894915,896792}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:08.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:904842,908178}Darn! Quit scampering around!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:25.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:922025,925028}After her!\NSt. Tail has entered the mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.24,0:15:32.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931243,932953}Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:35.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:933579,935456}Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:50.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:947050,950679}It can't be.\NI'm sure it was this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:06.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:963650,966153}St. Tail, you're in full view.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:11.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969698,971658}Give yourself up, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:15.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:971909,975162}It's unforgivable\Nto take someone's memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:28.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:985339,988425}I've got you cornered, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:30.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:988675,990594}You! Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:39.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:996099,999019}Wait a minute!\NWhat are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:43.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:999228,1003941}With all this weight,\Nthe chandelier is gonna fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:49.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007653,1009488}There!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.25,0:17:03.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021250,1023794}That's where it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:08.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024378,1028465}St. Tail, I'll have you\Nshow me your identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:16.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1033929,1036682}That idiot! At a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.93,0:17:18.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036932,1038100}Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:27.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041853,1047401}If I get rid of this mansion,\Nthere's nothing St. Tail can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:34.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052281,1054283}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:39.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056076,1059162}I won't let you destroy any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.70,0:17:45.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063709,1065752}It's…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:48.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066128,1068797}…Show…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:52.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070799,1072884}…Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:55.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073969,1075721}You pesky worm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:16.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090819,1096116}Exactly what I was worried about.\NHe's getting licked! Darn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:25.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101705,1105834}Goodbye. And I've got\Nthe jewelry box of memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.71,0:18:27.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1106710,1107836}Memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:31.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108295,1111632}What do you mean, memories, St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:36.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111882,1116720}Hey, what are you doing here?\NHold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:46.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122684,1126063}– And where are you going?\N– Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.35,0:18:51.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129358,1131902}– Hey, son!\N– Dad? Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:55.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132152,1135656}I had business with these two.\NNegoro and Momochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:58.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135906,1138992}– You're under arrest for fraud.\N– Fraud?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:02.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139242,1142287}These two are convicted criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:05.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142537,1145415}We already know\Nthat you two teamed up…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,0:19:09.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1145666,1149002}…to swindle this mansion\Nfrom Mr. Misaki. Give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.54,0:19:10.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149544,1150754}Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.51,0:19:26.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162516,1166895}– Mother, here, some water.\N– Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.48,0:19:38.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177489,1178782}I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:45.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179032,1185205}Father, my treasure box has come back!\NMy precious memories are back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.83,0:19:54.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190836,1194715}I'm glad! Then Michiru's able\Nto return to that house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:19:59.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195257,1199010}Yes. It's only natural because\Nthose two have been caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.21,0:20:01.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199219,1201722}But the house has\Nbeen damaged so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:06.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202389,1206143}Don't worry.\NThe memories haven't been damaged!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:20.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219614,1220866}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:24.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221450,1224703}I've heard that you've made\Na few more memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:29.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1224953,1229583}Memories! Quit bugging me about them!\NYou act just like someone I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:31.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1230375,1231835}Someone you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.08,0:20:36.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232085,1236798}Well, who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:41.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1237632,1241428}Oh, forget it!\NIt's none of your concern!
