Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:21:00.69,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1254232,1260697}If you asked me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:07.07,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1261698,1267078}before we shared our first kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:14.08,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1267537,1274085}for the reason I was crying,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:20.05,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1275128,1280050}I don't know what I'd say.
